==============================================
1. pod
    A pod is one or more container (A running docker image)
2. Pod - Gets wrapped into a Replica Set
    (It controls the number of ports e.g replicates the running Pod)
3. Replica Set Gets wrapped into a Deployment

4. All this gets wrapped in a yaml file

